<font color="#FF0000">MILITARY INDUSTRIAL COMPLEX</font><br>
<tt>Sat Mar 15 16:53:08 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Eisenhower warned us of the &quot;military industrial complex&quot;.  Surely you guys miss the point,(liberal vs. conservative; communism vs. capitalism).  The issue is one of technological developments making people unnecessary in the conduct of warfare. Warfare in the 21st century will not be conducted by men. The Vietnam &quot;Conflict&quot;, and the American public's opposition to that war, I contend, signified that it was the last bloody battlefield Americans would allow themselves to be placed upon by the military industrial complex. 
